&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve successfully reproduced this problem and would like to address it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d like to suggest&#160;an&#160;approach to resolve this issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add proper validation to the `&lt;tt&gt;getShortCanonicalName(String canonicalName)&lt;/tt&gt;` method&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Implement checks to ensure input conforms to JVM class name specifications&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Throw clear `&lt;tt&gt;IllegalArgumentException`&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;with descriptive messages for invalid inputs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Additionally, I will add unit test cases to cover edge scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How does that sound to you? I will commit the changes as soon as I&apos;ve completed the implementation and testing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
